### ðŸ”§ Merge All PHP Files from Git Dump

After using `git-dumper`, run this to combine all `.php` files from the dumped `.git` folder into one file for easier searching and analysis:

OUTPUT="merged_php_code.php"

find <path_to_git_dump> -type f -name "*.php" | while read file; do
  echo "===== $file =====" >> "$OUTPUT"
  cat "$file" >> "$OUTPUT"
  echo -e "\n\n" >> "$OUTPUT"
done
